T1  - The entrepreneurial ecosystem clock keeps on ticking – A replication and extension of Coad and Srhoj (2023)
AU  - van Dijk, Jasper
AU  - Leendertse, Jip
AU  - Stam, Erik
AU  - van Rijnsoever, Frank
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 2
SP  - 105154
